<C>__{pentangeli}
<D>__{i can't believe that out of thirty professional musicians, not one of you is italian!}
<P>__{(as the musicians laugh)}
<D>__{c'mon, give us a tarantella.}
<A>__{he waves his hands, conducting, and singing. the piano starts a vamp, the drums uncertainly join in. a clarinet starts to play "pop goes the weasel," and soon the rest of the orchestra is playing that. they look to pentangeli for approval. disgusted, he goes back to his table, eating a handful of canapes.}
